<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>3742</hymn_number>
<author>d/ zkryạ ʿwḍ ạllh, rynạ wdyʿ</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạ ḥbybạaⁿ mạt ʿny bạlṣlyb dẖbt mn ạ̉jly tryny ḥb qlbk
 wạ̉nạ ạlgẖạrq fy bḥr dẖnwby jỷt tfdy tbt rby bḥbk
 mt mʿk bạlṣlyb ʿn dẖnwby yạ ṭbyby kyf ạ̉brạ̉t ʿywby ?
 2- qd sẖrbt ạlkạ̉s mrạaⁿ yạ ḥbyby bl tḥmlt ạlhwạn dẖạk ʿạry
 bl tkllt bạ̹klyl rhyb tlk ạ̉sẖwạk dẖnwby mtẖl nạr
 qd ḥmlt ạlʿạr wạlnạr ḥbyby tftdy ạlnfs bạ̉hwạl ạlṣlyb
 3- rạỷʿ ḥbk yạ rby yswʿ ạ̹dẖ ṭlbt ạlṣfḥ ʿmn qd sẖjạk
 ạ̹nh ạlḥb ạlsmạwy ạlrfyʿ dmk ymḥw wmạ ạ̉gẖly̱ dmạk
 ( yạ ḥbyby ạ̹n qlby kskyb fy sjwd dạỷm lk ḥbyby )2</lyrics>
<title>yạ ḥbybạaⁿ mạt ʿny</title>
</song>